{"title":"Ekoi Road Helmets Get Unique Koroyd Protection Debut at the Tour de France","link":"https://bikerumor.com/ekoi-road-helmets-get-unique-koroyd-protection-debut-at-the-tour-de-france/","date":1689010724000,"content":"<p>In the biggest race of the year, four Pro Tour teams have been racing for the past week and a half with a couple of new Ekoi road helmets equipped with Koroyd protection tech – Cofidis, Arkéa Samsic, Lotto Dstny &amp; Israel – Premier Tech. The iconic plastic honeycomb layer tech will now boost impact protection in the new aero Aerodinamica and lightweight Stradale, while providing increased heat dissipation of the rider’s head.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Ekoi Koroyd-equipped road bike helmets at the Tour de France</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-sponsores-stage-wins-at-2023-Tour-de-France.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"920\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-sponsores-stage-wins-at-2023-Tour-de-France.jpg\" alt=\"Ekoi aero road bike helmets at 2023 Tour de France, Stage wins\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-sponsores-stage-wins-at-2023-Tour-de-France.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-sponsores-stage-wins-at-2023-Tour-de-France-297x152.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-sponsores-stage-wins-at-2023-Tour-de-France-800x409.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-sponsores-stage-wins-at-2023-Tour-de-France-120x61.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-sponsores-stage-wins-at-2023-Tour-de-France-768x393.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-sponsores-stage-wins-at-2023-Tour-de-France-1536x785.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption><em>2023 TdF Stage 2 winner Victor LaFay Cofidis &amp; Stage 9 winner Michael Woods of Israel – Premier Tech, c. Ekoi</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Two stage winners at this summer’s Tour de France have already crossed the finish line first wearing Ekoi helmets –  Victor LaFay of Cofidis on Stage 2 and then Michael Woods of Israel – Premier Tech on Stage 9 –  albeit with the current non-Koroyd AR14 aero helmet. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stage-4-sprint-finish-courtesy-of-ASO.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stage-4-sprint-finish-courtesy-of-ASO.jpg\" alt=\"Ekoi Koroyd road bike helmets at 2023 Tour de France, sprint finish\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stage-4-sprint-finish-courtesy-of-ASO.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stage-4-sprint-finish-courtesy-of-ASO-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stage-4-sprint-finish-courtesy-of-ASO-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stage-4-sprint-finish-courtesy-of-ASO-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stage-4-sprint-finish-courtesy-of-ASO-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stage-4-sprint-finish-courtesy-of-ASO-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption><em>TdF Stage 4 finish c. ASO</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>But Caleb Ewan of Lotto Dstny has going hard and been close to victory – sprinting to 3rd in Stage 3, then 2nd in Stage 4 in sprints behind Jasper Philipsen – wearing the latest Koroyd-equipped Ekoi Aerodinamica aero road helmet. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stage-7-courtesy-of-ASO_photo-by-Jered-and-Ashley-Gruber.jpg\"><img width=\"1600\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stage-7-courtesy-of-ASO_photo-by-Jered-and-Ashley-Gruber.jpg\" alt=\"Ekoi Koroyd road bike helmets at 2023 Tour de France, lightweight Stradale\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stage-7-courtesy-of-ASO_photo-by-Jered-and-Ashley-Gruber.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stage-7-courtesy-of-ASO_photo-by-Jered-and-Ashley-Gruber-297x186.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stage-7-courtesy-of-ASO_photo-by-Jered-and-Ashley-Gruber-800x500.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stage-7-courtesy-of-ASO_photo-by-Jered-and-Ashley-Gruber-120x75.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stage-7-courtesy-of-ASO_photo-by-Jered-and-Ashley-Gruber-768x480.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stage-7-courtesy-of-ASO_photo-by-Jered-and-Ashley-Gruber-1536x960.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption><em>TdF Stage 7 c. ASO, photo by Jered &amp; Ashley Gruber</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>When the race entered the mountains, we also spotted a number of Israel – Premier Tech riders with the lighter, more open-vented Stradale.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Koroyd tech inside</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Aerdinamica_x-ray.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Aerdinamica_x-ray.jpg\" alt=\"Ekoi Koroyd road bike helmets at 2023 Tour de France, aero Aerdinamica x-ray\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Aerdinamica_x-ray.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Aerdinamica_x-ray-297x165.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Aerdinamica_x-ray-800x444.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Aerdinamica_x-ray-120x67.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Aerdinamica_x-ray-768x427.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Aerdinamica_x-ray-1536x853.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Ekoi says they partnered with Koroyd to benefit from increased rider protection over conventional light in-mold EPS foam construction, without sacrificing on weight or ventilation. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Bastien-Lemaire-Ekoi-Aerodinamica.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Bastien-Lemaire-Ekoi-Aerodinamica.jpg\" alt=\"Ekoi Koroyd road bike helmets at 2023 Tour de France, aero Aerdinamica side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Bastien-Lemaire-Ekoi-Aerodinamica.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Bastien-Lemaire-Ekoi-Aerodinamica-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Bastien-Lemaire-Ekoi-Aerodinamica-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Bastien-Lemaire-Ekoi-Aerodinamica-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Bastien-Lemaire-Ekoi-Aerodinamica-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Bastien-Lemaire-Ekoi-Aerodinamica-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Bastien-Lemaire-Ekoi-Aerodinamica-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a><figcaption><em>c. Ekoi</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>“<em>There’s a lot of stress in the peloton, especially during major events such as the Grand Tours or the Classics, which is why we wanted to work on safety in the event of a crash</em>,” said Jean-Christophe Rattel, Ekoi CEO. “<em>We approached Koroyd because we saw their concept to be the best way of optimizing the protection in our helmet.”</em></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Tech Details – What do we know?</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Aerdinamica-rear.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Aerdinamica-rear.jpg\" alt=\"Ekoi Koroyd road bike helmets at 2023 Tour de France, aero Aerdinamica\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Aerdinamica-rear.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Aerdinamica-rear-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Aerdinamica-rear-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Aerdinamica-rear-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Aerdinamica-rear-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Aerdinamica-rear-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Ekoï describes the new Aerodinamica as their “pinnacle aero helmet, integrated with KOROYD for the ultimate in impact protection and advanced breathability”. Developed together with Italian aero specialist design firm Pininfarina, the Aerodinamica features just three vertical vents across a smooth front, no top or side vents, and a chopped-off aerodynamic tail cone shape revealing a large rear exhaust port. It looks a lot like a scaled-back aero TT helmet adapted for more versatile road riding.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stradale_x-ray.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stradale_x-ray.jpg\" alt=\"Ekoi Koroyd road bike helmets at 2023 Tour de France, lightweight Stradale gets new tech inside\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stradale_x-ray.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stradale_x-ray-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stradale_x-ray-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stradale_x-ray-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stradale_x-ray-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stradale_x-ray-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new Stradale on the other hand, opts for a fully open approach for maximum ventilation – with a new Koroyd Connect Integration Solution. Here, you can see the plastic Koroyd honeycomb as it sits under the outer polycarbonate shell and top layer of EPS foam – but is also cut away at some fully open vents to allow direct airflow cooling vs. the Koroyd solutions we’ve seen with <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=Smith+Koroyd\" target=\"_blank\">Smith</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=Endura+Koroyd\" target=\"_blank\">Endura</a> helmets in the past.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>New Ekoi Koroyd helmet availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Aerdinamica-aero-road_Stradale-lightweight.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Aerdinamica-aero-road_Stradale-lightweight.jpg\" alt=\"Ekoi Koroyd road bike helmets at 2023 Tour de France, aero Aerdinamica &amp; lightweight Stradale,\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Aerdinamica-aero-road_Stradale-lightweight.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Aerdinamica-aero-road_Stradale-lightweight-297x119.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Aerdinamica-aero-road_Stradale-lightweight-800x320.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Aerdinamica-aero-road_Stradale-lightweight-120x48.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Aerdinamica-aero-road_Stradale-lightweight-768x307.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Aerdinamica-aero-road_Stradale-lightweight-1536x614.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Ekoi have technically debuted the two new Koroyd-equipped road helmets now that they’ve come out of hiding at the Tour de France, yet it’s really mostly just a teaser. We’ll still have to wait a while to get the full details, and you’ll have to wait a while until you can buy them direct from Ekoi. Official consumer availability is slated for September 2023, when we should get key data like pricing, weights, colors &amp; sizing.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stage-1-courtesy-of-ASO_photo-by-Jered-and-Ashley-Gruber.jpg\"><img width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stage-1-courtesy-of-ASO_photo-by-Jered-and-Ashley-Gruber.jpg\" alt=\"Ekoi Koroyd road bike helmets at 2023 Tour de France, aero Aerdinamica \" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stage-1-courtesy-of-ASO_photo-by-Jered-and-Ashley-Gruber.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stage-1-courtesy-of-ASO_photo-by-Jered-and-Ashley-Gruber-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stage-1-courtesy-of-ASO_photo-by-Jered-and-Ashley-Gruber-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stage-1-courtesy-of-ASO_photo-by-Jered-and-Ashley-Gruber-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stage-1-courtesy-of-ASO_photo-by-Jered-and-Ashley-Gruber-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Ekoi-Koroyd-road-bike-helmets-at-2023-Tour-de-France_Stage-1-courtesy-of-ASO_photo-by-Jered-and-Ashley-Gruber-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a><figcaption><em>TdF Stage 1 c. ASO, photo by Jered &amp; Ashley Gruber</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Until then, we just have to enjoy le Tour.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.ekoi.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Ekoi.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/ekoi-road-helmets-get-unique-koroyd-protection-debut-at-the-tour-de-france/\">Ekoi Road Helmets Get Unique Koroyd Protection Debut at the Tour de France</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"4310174283b21feb93aa74106fd8c36509077c46dfbdcd4ea9fbd17f2caaf2a9","category":"Cycling"}